    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1864年，在北极的某座未知岛屿上。船童山姆和忠诚的哈士奇艾莉被困在这片无情的极寒之地。你必须经受严酷的自然考验，揭开阴郁的谜团，在寻找归途的同时找回真正的自我。可单人操控两名角色，也可和好友协作求生。生死存亡，唯友谊可依！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/cccd23b74664776bbbbfe741f1ba8a2b.webp?t=1769174404\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/ca6dacfd94b75e6b5a2254f167bfd0c6.poster.avif?t=1769174404\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/ca6dacfd94b75e6b5a2254f167bfd0c6.webm?t=1769174404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/ca6dacfd94b75e6b5a2254f167bfd0c6.mp4?t=1769174404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Ikuma》是一部成长史诗，你要在这片陌生的土地上探索觅食、揭开谜团。这一切不仅为了生存，更是为了与过去和解，最终找到真正的自我。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/abbd0de1dfc48b90a7b47a1caa6d98c9.webp?t=1769174404\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/fe59a6187a05b02ce8f4bc27b4a0673b.poster.avif?t=1769174404\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/fe59a6187a05b02ce8f4bc27b4a0673b.webm?t=1769174404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/fe59a6187a05b02ce8f4bc27b4a0673b.mp4?t=1769174404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以随时在两个同伴之间切换，也可以与好友并肩游玩，充分发挥各个角色的技能，共同达成目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/1bf4e3b0493dae5102b6e6be2805567e.webp?t=1769174404\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/52c1f5993f19ae07d44ec926de12e188.poster.avif?t=1769174404\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/52c1f5993f19ae07d44ec926de12e188.webm?t=1769174404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/52c1f5993f19ae07d44ec926de12e188.mp4?t=1769174404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用在岛上收集到的工具和物品，在险峻地形中开辟生路。攀爬、钓鱼、收集资源，竭尽所能将自己和同伴带离绝境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/1b1482837935789a4f1a836cade32e58.webp?t=1769174404\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/450ce8fd6af27cd4d17ae183349cbaf4.poster.avif?t=1769174404\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/450ce8fd6af27cd4d17ae183349cbaf4.webm?t=1769174404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728620/extras/450ce8fd6af27cd4d17ae183349cbaf4.mp4?t=1769174404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探寻因纽特人的古老传说，揭开有关失落探险队的谜团。追寻他们的足迹，但要当心，在浓雾笼罩的道路上，正潜伏着未知的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅  壯美的極地環境：從危機四伏的冰川洞穴到被遺忘的冰封古船，利用你能找到的有限工具，穿越攝人心魄的北極絕景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅  魂牽夢縈的謎團：蒐集線索，揭開冰蓋之下那支被詛咒的探險隊的終極命運。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅  孤軍奮戰或協作求生：與好友共赴極地征途，並肩對抗嚴酷北極的重重考驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅  極地生存：管理有限補給，在刺骨嚴寒中掙扎求生，與你忠實的雪橇犬相依為命，踏上歸家之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅  屢獲殊榮的敘事冒險遊戲《Lost Ember》原班人馬，再度奉上這場直擊靈魂的全新震撼旅程</p>",
